### Inventory Service API Tests

@host = http://localhost:8084/api/v1/inventory
@token = Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Crear Inventario inicial (SKU: KB-MECH-RGB)
POST {{host}}
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "skuCode": "KB-MECH-RGB",
  "quantity": 100
}

### 2. Crear Inventario inicial (SKU: MOUSE-WL-20K)
POST {{host}}
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "skuCode": "MOUSE-WL-20K",
  "quantity": 50
}

### 3. Obtener Inventario por SKU
GET {{host}}/KB-MECH-RGB
Authorization: {{token}}

### 4. Listar Todo el Inventario
GET {{host}}
Authorization: {{token}}

### 5. Verificar si hay stock (Disponible: true)
GET {{host}}/KB-MECH-RGB/in-stock?quantity=5
Authorization: {{token}}

### 6. Verificar si hay stock (Insuficiente: false)
GET {{host}}/KB-MECH-RGB/in-stock?quantity=200
Authorization: {{token}}

### 7. Probar Error 404 (SKU inexistente)
GET {{host}}/NON-EXISTENT-SKU
Authorization: {{token}}
